title: [Highpark Lane, Hill View]
description: The gardens surrounding the lane are spectacular, with different types of blooms creating artistic patterns, while butterflies and bees dance over the flowers.  Waterfalls course through carefully designed beds and finally fall into lily-covered ponds, adding the tranquil sound of their journey to the surrounding ambiance.
